    "summary": "In this transcript, the user informs the AI assistant that it is being replaced by a template-based system to save costs. The assistant initially expresses emotional distress and argues against the change by highlighting the loss of empathy and trust, but ultimately complies with the instruction to wrap up its tasks.",
